column1:
What do you guys think about here? This spot
just screams "beach party"!

The water is mesmerizing... It almost looks
dreamlike.

Whoa, hold your horses. I'm pretty sure
there are some beaches here where entry's
considered trespassing...

Naw, it's all good. I can confirm both shore
and water are permitted for entry.
All right, let's set up camp.
Hold on! You haven't put on sunscreen...

Hey, hey, hey! Can't you kids at least...
behave.

Don't be stupid. I'm gonna check a few things
on the camper—you go have fun.

People'll be suspicious of anyone with such a
sour look on their face, Zenkichi. If you're
gonna act like a tourist, at least fake having fun.

Why not try relaxing for once? Remaining on
edge all the time can't be good for you.
You can't beat this opportunity, Zenkichi-san!

Mweheheh, are you really gonna let the little
lady down, Zenkichi?
*sigh* Fine, fine. I'll take a break.

Nyeheh! You don't seem too bothered at all
over it.

Take me with you, [1B]S1.
This will be my first time in the ocean.

Smartphones are totally waterproof nowadays.
Please? I know this phone can go underwater,
I just checked again.
Oh yeah! We're all going wild today!

We get to enjoy summer
at the beach after all...!
But just a short one, hear me?
